<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    {% with title='Confirmation of Canonical CLA Submission' %}
        {% include 'partials/head.j2' %}
    {% endwith %}
    <body>
        {% include 'partials/logo.j2' %}
        <h1>Confirmation of Canonical Contributor License Agreement Submission</h1>
        <p>Dear {{ contributor_name }},</p>
        <p>
            Thank you for submitting the Canonical Contributor License Agreement (CLA)
            {% if is_organization %}for your organization, {{ organization_name }}{% endif %}
            . We appreciate your commitment to contributing to our open-source projects.
        </p>
        {% if is_organization %}
            <p>
                Our community team will review your submission and contact you if any additional information is required. Once approved, contributors from your organization using email addresses with the domain <strong>{{ email_domain }}</strong> will be recognized as having signed the CLA.
            </p>
        {% else %}
            <p>Your CLA has been recorded in our system. You can now contribute to Canonical projects under this agreement.</p>
        {% endif %}
        <p>
            If you need to make any changes to your submission or have any questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contributor-agreement@canonical.com">contributor-agreement@canonical.com</a>.
        </p>
        <p>Thank you for your contribution to the open-source community!</p>
        <p>
            Best regards,
            <br />
            The Canonical Team
        </p>
    </body>
</html>
